=head1 DESCRIPTION

This action to delivers an email to a mailbox.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 ActionFailurePolicy => Str

A policy that states what to do in the case of failure. The action will
fail if there are configuration errors. For example, the mailbox ARN is
no longer valid.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> MailboxArn => Str

The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of a WorkMail organization to deliver
the email to.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> RoleArn => Str

The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of an IAM role to use to execute this
action. The role must have access to the workmail:DeliverToMailbox API.



